text = "[b]Butler[/b] is itch.io's command-line tool for uploading games.

[b][color=#6bcfff]Installation[/color][/b]

1. Download from: [url]https://itch.io/docs/butler/[/url]
2. Extract and add to your system PATH
   Or place in: %USERPROFILE%/.config/itch/bin/

[b][color=#6bcfff]First-Time Setup[/color][/b]

After installing butler, you must log in:

1. Open a terminal/command prompt
2. Run: [code]butler login[/code]
3. A browser window will open
4. Log in to your itch.io account
5. Return to godot-valet and click Publish

[b][color=#6bcfff]Verification[/color][/b]

To verify butler is installed correctly:
[code]butler --version[/code]

[b][color=#ffcc66]Note:[/color][/b] Butler must be logged in before publishing. The login session persists, so you only need to do this once per machine."
